<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Sonminsooo</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../../images/icon/instagram-16x16.ico">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/FindPassword.css">
<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/961742c2a3.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src = "../../js/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/jquery.serializejson.min.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/SendEmail.css">
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$.ajax({
		url : '/Sonminsooo/LoginUser.do',
		type : 'post',
		success : function(res){
			msg = "계정에 다시 로그인할 수 있는 링크가 포함된 이메일을 <span>"+ res.mem_email + "</span>주소로 보내드렸습니다.";
			$('.PWOKmsg p').html(msg);
			
		},
		error : function(xhr){
			console.log("상태 : " + xhr.status);
		},
		dataType : 'json'
	}) 
	
	$('#OTHLG').on('click', function(){
		
		$('#otherLogin').modal('show');
		
	})
	$('.LGObtn').on('click', function(){		
		location.href = "findpassword.html";
	})
	
	$('.PWOK').on('click', function(){
		location.href = "findpassword.html";
	})
	
	$('#next').on('click', function(){
		$('.apiDIV').hide();
		$('.FPW').show();
	})
	
	
})


</script>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- Modal -->
  <div id="otherLogin" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
    
      <!-- Modal content-->
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h4>로그아웃하시겠어요?</h4>
          <span>계정에서 로그아웃하시겠어요?</span>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <button type="button" class="Mb LGObtn" data-dismiss="modal">로그아웃</button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="Mb CNEbtn" data-dismiss="modal">취소</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
  


<nav class="header">
	<div class="header wrap">
		<div class="logoarea">
			<a href="loginpage.html" target="_self">
			 <img src="../../images/icon/logo.png" alt="logo.png">
			</a> 
		</div>
		
		<div>
		  <input type="button" id="OTHLG" value="다른 계정으로 로그인">
		</div>
	</div>			
</nav>


  <div class="MILG apiDIV">
   <div class="dall title"><span>로그인하려면 본인 확인을 진행해주세요</span></div>
   <div class="dall bc">회원님의 계정에서 비정상적인 활동이 감지되어 로그아웃했습니다.</div>
   <div class="dall bc">비활성화되기 전에 계정에 다시 로그인하려면 1일 이내에 다음 단계를 완료하세요.</div>
   <div id="google_recaptha">
    <script src='https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js' async defer></script>
    <div class="g-recaptcha" data-sitekey="6Ld6HN0cAAAAAMIQJxu1Ycr_kVK7B7bhtF5GKeYr" data-callback="recaptcha"></div>
   </div>
   
   <div class="aplNext">
     <input id="next" type="button" value="다음"> <!-- disabled -->
   </div>
  </div>


 <div class="MILG FPW" style="display:none">
   <div class="msp">이메일 전송됨</div>
   <div class="PWOKmsg"> 
     <p></p>    
   </div>
   <input class="PWOK" type="button" value="확인"> 
 </div>

<a hidden="hidden" 
   href="mailto:name@naver.com?subject=user님, 더욱 간편하게 Instagram에 다시 로그인해보세요 ">메일보내기</a>




</body>
</html>




















